snippet.title: The Interval [Reload Magazine Game Jam 012] - Out now!
snippet.description:
It's out - go play it now! http://sean-noonan.itch.io/interval

Let us know what you think! I'm going to take a little break before finishing the post jam version. I've got a new computer and I want to spend some time with it!

Thanks for playing!

Want to find out more? Join the Discord: https://discord.gg/rSyQths

Web: http://noonan.design
Twitter: http://twitter.com/SeanNoonan

#gamedev #gamejam #EFPSE
